---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="LoopController">
  <h1>LoopController</h1>

  <p>The orchestration engine that runs the full generate evaluate refine loop until the agent passes or max iterations are reached.</p>

  <h2>Interface</h2>
  <pre><code>import &lcub; LoopController &rcub; from "agent-forge/loop_controller";
import &lcub; createOllamaBackend &rcub; from "agent-forge/llm_backend/ollama";

const llm = createOllamaBackend();
const controller = new LoopController(llm);

const result = await controller.run(&lcub;
  description: "review PRs for logic errors",
  name: "pr_reviewer",
  tools: ["gh_api", "read_file"],
  threshold: 0.85,
  maxIterations: 5,
&rcub;);

// result.state: "DONE" or "FAILED"
// result.passed: boolean
// result.finalScore: number or undefined
// result.bestScore: number or undefined
// result.iterations: number
// result.agentId: string or undefined
// result.versionId: string or undefined</code></pre>

  <h2>State Machine</h2>
  <pre><code>IDLE
  (run() called)
 GENERATING
  (schema generated)
 EVALUATING
  (eval complete)
 REFINING
  (refinement done, back to EVALUATING)
  ... loop until:
    DONE (passed gate)
    FAILED (max iterations)</code></pre>

  <h2>Loop Algorithm</h2>
  <pre><code>for (iter = 1; iter less-or-equal maxIterations; iter++) &lcub;
  if (iter equals 1 and not currentCode) &lcub;
    // First iteration: generate
    currentCode = Generator.make(description)
  &rcub; else if (currentCode) &lcub;
    // Subsequent: evaluate before refining
    TestCases = TestGenerator.generate(description)
    Report = Evaluator.run(agentCode, TestCases)
    Coverage = TestGenerator.checkCoverage(TestCases)
    Report.coverageGaps = Coverage.gaps

    if (QualityGate.check(Report).passed) &lcub;
      return &lcub; state: DONE, passed: true, finalScore: Report.composite &rcub;
    &rcub;

    // Refine and loop
    currentCode = Refiner.refine(agentCode, Report)
  &rcub;
&rcub;
return &lcub; state: FAILED, passed: false, bestScore &rcub;</code></pre>

  <h2>Best Score Tracking</h2>
  <p>The highest-scoring version is tracked across all iterations. If the loop exits without passing, the best version's code is still available in the registry for inspection.</p>

  <h2>Integration with Registry</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Agent created (or looked up if exists) on first iteration</li>
    <li>Every iteration creates a new <code>agent_versions</code> row</li>
    <li>Every iteration creates an <code>eval_runs</code> row with full failure report</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Exit States</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>State</th><th>Meaning</th><th>Export?</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>DONE</td><td>Agent passed QualityGate</td><td>Yes</td></tr>
      <tr><td>FAILED</td><td>Max iterations reached</td><td>No</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</Layout>
